text: <color=#FFE787>Response time: </color><color=#ccffcc>$Skill_CD(2526)@</color> Summon 2 blood wheels, fly out from the generals back and forth, with <color=#ccffcc> $Skill_Str(2526)@</color><color=#80cc00>War</color> causes physical damage to the enemy.
